there.

1464
01:10:55,872 --> 01:10:58,461
Although you were the first
person to hit me in the face.

1465
01:10:58,495 --> 01:10:59,807
- I was.

1466
01:10:59,841 --> 01:11:00,877
- We used to be friends.

1467
01:11:00,911 --> 01:11:02,154
What happened to us?

1468
01:11:02,188 --> 01:11:03,155
- Girl plague.

1469
01:11:03,189 --> 01:11:05,088
You know that female
competitive thing

1470
01:11:05,122 --> 01:11:09,610
that kicks in somewhere between
middle school and death?

1471
01:11:09,644 --> 01:11:10,680
- I am sorry.

1472
01:11:10,714 --> 01:11:12,751
I know you think I'm
crazy and that I'm trying

1473
01:11:12,785 --> 01:11:16,962
to ruin your life and I would
explain my twisted rationale

1474
01:11:18,308 --> 01:11:19,792
but you wouldn't believe
it unless you were six

1475
01:11:19,827 --> 01:11:22,070
and waiting for Santa Clause.

1476
01:11:22,105 --> 01:11:24,280
- What is it with this time of
year?

1477
01:11:24,314 --> 01:11:25,867
- Brings out the worst in
everyone.

1478
01:11:25,902 --> 01:11:27,041
- I don't know why we do it to
ourselves

1479
01:11:27,075 --> 01:11:29,354
