is open a bottle of wine, sit
on a beach,

1486
01:11:41,538 --> 01:11:45,956
and thank god that we weren't
born in the Middle Ages.

1487
01:11:45,991 --> 01:11:49,305
- Yeah but the corsets were
kind of hot.

1488
01:11:50,202 --> 01:11:51,030
- Well.

1489
01:11:52,722 --> 01:11:54,240
- This is the worst Christmas
ever.

1490
01:11:54,275 --> 01:11:56,484
- At least you got the guy.

1491
01:11:59,936 --> 01:12:01,144
- Really?

1492
01:12:01,178 --> 01:12:03,836
- Yeah, Dave still has a thing
for you.

1493
01:12:03,871 --> 01:12:05,597
He confessed.

1494
01:12:05,631 --> 01:12:07,081
And I think you should go for
it.

1495
01:12:07,115 --> 01:12:08,358
It's okay.

1496
01:12:08,393 --> 01:12:12,569
Weirdly, very weirdly, I kinda
think that Jake Lasky's cute.

1497
01:12:14,985 --> 01:12:16,401
- I could so hook you up.

1498
01:12:16,435 --> 01:12:17,436
- Oh really?

1499
01:12:18,575 --> 01:12:20,405
Happy New Year Marcia.

1500
